Oliver  Ratzesberger 
Executive Compensation
As EVP and Chief Product Officer at TERADATA CORP, Oliver  Ratzesberger  made $2,312,507 in total compensation.  Of this total $434,719 was received as a salary, $429,675 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,431,715 was awarded as stock and $16,398 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


